			<div class="cd-timeline-content" style="background-color: #ddffdd">
				<h2>v1.2.0: Reporting pipeline</h2>
				<p>Nanoverse v1.2.0 will introduce a flexible platform for creating custom reports. These reports can capture properties of individual agents, system-level aggregate statistics, or even properties of each simulation in a repeated experiment. Like the visualization engine, the reports will be built up through a series of functional transformations.</p>
			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->
		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->

		<div class="cd-timeline-block">
