				<h2>v2.0.0: Design by cartoon</h2>
				<p>The second version of Nanoverse will introduce a visual environment for building and exploring models through visual cues. This visual programming interface will eliminate the need for computer code altogether, allowing subject-area experts to focus their attention on the model at hand.</p>
			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->
