				<h2>v3.0.0: Compile-to-Java</h2>
				<p>Prior to v3.0.0, Nanoverse will have the ability to translate Nanosyntax directly to source code in the <a href="https://www.java.com/">Java</a> computer language. In addition to providing speed and efficiency boosts, direct translation will allow users to customize their simulation beyond the limits of the Nanoverse platform, as well as to produce stand-alone products for business and entertainment.</p>
